# Test Plan

## 1. Scope
- List what is being tested in this round.

## 2. Test Strategy
- Overall approach: manual / automated / mixed

## 3. Environment
- Test environment requirements.

## 4. Schedule
- Estimated start and end.

## 5. Entry Criteria
- Conditions that must be met before testing begins.

## 6. Exit Criteria
- Conditions that define testing as complete:
  - All test cases executed
  - Zero open bugs of severity >= medium
  - Sign-off obtained
